{"tid":2134850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（全民不合作檢測）新疆疑藉體檢收集維吾爾人DNA","createTime":"2020-08-01T04:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:07:42.000Z","uid":222970,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"693e7c472610a77fe67c0056bee7bdcb37b0c34a","tid":2134850,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=338470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338470&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=abbc9f01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338470&h=d533ab66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=338470</a><br />\n<br />\n新疆疑藉體檢收集維吾爾人DNA<br />\n<br />\n2019年2月22日 15:12 <br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新疆近年推行「全民體檢」計劃，一直有聲音質疑當局假借檢查名義，大規模收集維吾爾族DNA樣本，加強監控。當地基因測序設備主要供應商，來自美國的生物科技公司決定，終止向新疆銷售相關產品。<br />\n<br />\n全民體檢計劃在新疆實施約三年多。官方數據顯示，單是2016至2017年間，有近3600萬民眾參與。<br />\n<br />\n有別於一般體檢，免費檢查項目包括採集血液、指紋、掃瞄容貌、虹膜，甚或錄音等，計劃理論上屬自願性質，但也有受地方幹部、公安施壓，強制接受檢查的例子。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織一直質疑，<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>政府以檢查之名，收集維吾爾人的DNA與其他生物識別數據編制數據庫，以便監控可疑人物。<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n計劃所需硬件如基因測序設備，以及用作比對的DNA樣本等，據報得到美國協助。其中，主要設備供應商為總部設於馬薩諸塞州的生物技術公司「賽默飛世爾科技」。公司2017年年報顯示，該年度中國銷售額約為20億美元，佔整體收入一成。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，購入的儀器部分交予公安廳使用，將透過體檢收集得來的DNA，與不同族群的樣本作比對，<br />\n<br />\n以分辨維吾爾族人基因排序，比對樣本由耶魯大學遺傳學者基德提供。報道指，他曾應公安部邀請訪華，建立交情。<br />\n<br />\n新疆當局否認安排全民體檢另有目的，又指採購的DNA測序儀只作內部用途，牽涉其中的美國企業與學者一概否認知悉其設備、樣本等或被濫用。<br />\n<br />\n不過，隨着維吾爾族被打壓的證據逐漸浮面，美國國內關注聲浪越發高漲。輿論壓力下，賽默飛世爾科技周三宣布，不再向新疆銷售基因測序儀等設備，承諾配合美國當局徹查事件。"},{"pid":"1cac35ae1fa49aeb3aa85d22c8770643fe937846","tid":2134850,"uid":109345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"比貓貓狗狗既DNA佢<br />\n<br />\n申：無寵物"},{"pid":"73527c280e723f250c3c55f230675a043c75ca97","tid":2134850,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaaa0b3b6776abc0071ed331578463806cbf25c","tid":2134850,"uid":49747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/organ-10062017075527.html/Organ.png/@@images/7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Forgan-10062017075527.html%2FOrgan.png%2F%40%40images%2F7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png&h=ac45736e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg&h=e4e1ad4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好快香港機場見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cb5126e020bcc5bf44e81d6984f3fe917b83b7","tid":2134850,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a1ca821f9ba5ea1bba848089bfbd4e4d45848fa7","tid":2134850,"uid":13176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">【大規模檢測 = DNA數據庫？】<br />\n<br />\n中共將會派人黎香港進行大型檢測，雖則以防疫為由，但司馬昭之心路人皆知。<br />\n<br />\n我地見坊間有人提醒市民應該盡快進行檢測，避免被採集DNA。但唔好意思，依家政府所提供嘅「一站式」檢測服務已經足以採集大家嘅DNA。<br />\n<br />\n係7月17日，食環署委派咗一間叫Prenetics嘅生物科技公司，提供「一站式」檢測服務。<br />\n<br />\n雖然Prenetics創於香港，但獲阿里巴巴等紅資投資足足4000萬USD。佢地主打圓基因技術（Circle DNA），提供基因檢測服務。用佢地提供嘅檢測套裝，一滴口水就可以檢測到DNA，佢地仲係屈臣氏嘅廣告中聲稱一滴口水可以測試超過500個檢測項目添。電視見到好多人排隊等嘅病毒檢測服務，就係用緊佢地嘅Circle DNA技術。<br />\n<br />\n根據《華爾街日報》係17年嘅報導，中国某啲地區當中，執法部門已經將人民嘅DNA資料同其他生物特徵資訊一齊儲存，包括指紋、肖像、聲紋，並將人民嘅日常舉動（如：網上購物記錄、娛樂習慣）連結埋一齊，方便公安監視人民之餘，並成功透過此舉破案。<br />\n<br />\n而根據XG01係19年一篇關於美國警方透過DNA破案嘅報導，佢地整咗一張圖解釋DNA點樣協助警方破案，方便大家瞭解當中嘅來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABnizOx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABnizOx.jpg&h=21d6c2b6&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d601f6ee8eac2a1ebd39e3edbdb6104ea5f77a97","tid":2134850,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9484082fe22d5c811aa24c1a021a805bb50c7d29","tid":2134850,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aaaa0b3b6776abc0071ed331578463806cbf25c","tid":2134850,"uid":49747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/organ-10062017075527.html/Organ.png/@@images/7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Forgan-10062017075527.html%2FOrgan.png%2F%40%40images%2F7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png&h=ac45736e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg&h=e4e1ad4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好快香港機場見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab25a2e644fbe5f18adf35daf5e5ca32951d7d6a","tid":2134850,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f25769f79152113560d1590b0ddf36ff2ebec8","tid":2134850,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91a61315cd54b25505f30a1a32851a966a4d78d","tid":2134850,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"當地基因測序設備主要供應商，來自美國的生物科技公司決定，終止向新疆銷售相關產品。<br />\n<br />\n美國公司助長支共迫害維吾爾人"},{"pid":"803e71f8668823e02f5372c1a2206888f65aa14b","tid":2134850,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9484082fe22d5c811aa24c1a021a805bb50c7d29","tid":2134850,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aaaa0b3b6776abc0071ed331578463806cbf25c","tid":2134850,"uid":49747,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/organ-10062017075527.html/Organ.png/@@images/7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Forgan-10062017075527.html%2FOrgan.png%2F%40%40images%2F7b692b28-94e7-4a73-93f9-cc50e26a78e8.png&h=ac45736e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F850a214c57367a88c08fd6ad1a79cfa4-800x450.jpg&h=e4e1ad4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好快香港機場見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"高鐵站都得啫&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"92ebe3ce7d2ba0a1d76af84184b65fcee918a36d","tid":2134850,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}